sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Envoy Gateway<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant BBR as Body Based Router<br/>9004/TCP gRPC
    participant EPP as Endpoint Picker<br/>9002/TCP gRPC
    participant ModelServer as Model Server Pod<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant TrainSrv as Latency Training<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant PredSrv as Latency Prediction<br/>8001/TCP HTTP

    Note over Client,ModelServer: Flow 1: Inference Request Routing

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP (or TLS at gateway)
    Gateway->>BBR: ext-proc: ProcessingRequest<br/>gRPC (optional TLS)
    BBR->>BBR: Parse body → extract "model" field<br/>Set X-Gateway-Model-Name header
    BBR-->>Gateway: ProcessingResponse<br/>(headers mutation)
    Gateway->>EPP: ext-proc: ProcessingRequest<br/>gRPC (optional TLS)
    EPP->>EPP: Flow Control check<br/>(priority queuing, admission)
    EPP->>EPP: Schedule endpoint<br/>(filter → score → pick)
    EPP-->>Gateway: ProcessingResponse<br/>(endpoint selection + headers)
    Gateway->>ModelServer: Forward request to<br/>selected endpoint (HTTP/H2C)
    ModelServer-->>Gateway: Inference response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over EPP,ModelServer: Flow 2: Model Server Metrics Scraping

    loop Every scrape interval
        EPP->>ModelServer: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP (InsecureSkipVerify default)
        ModelServer-->>EPP: Prometheus metrics<br/>(KV-cache, queue depth,<br/>running requests, LoRA info)
        EPP->>EPP: Update in-memory datastore
    end

    Note over EPP,PredSrv: Flow 3: Latency Prediction Pipeline (optional)

    EPP->>TrainSrv: POST training samples<br/>(observed latencies)<br/>HTTP 8000/TCP
    TrainSrv->>TrainSrv: Retrain XGBoost model<br/>(every 10s)
    PredSrv->>TrainSrv: Sync trained model files<br/>HTTP 8000/TCP (or shared PV)
    EPP->>PredSrv: POST prediction request<br/>(request features)<br/>HTTP 8001/TCP
    PredSrv-->>EPP: Predicted TTFT/TPOT

    Note over EPP,K8sAPI: Flow 4: CRD Watch & Reconciliation

    K8sAPI-->>EPP: Watch events:<br/>InferencePool, InferenceObjective,<br/>InferenceModelRewrite, Pods
    EPP->>EPP: Reconcile → update datastore<br/>(endpoint pool, priorities,<br/>rewrite rules)
